  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COVID-19 Internews: Strengthening Rural Radio for impartial information in DRC</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">COVID-19 St&#xE4;rkt landsbygdsradio f&#xF6;r opartisk information i Demokratiska republiken Kongo</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reprogrammed funds to address COVID-19
The project is designed to ensure a resilient, policy reforms, digitally-enabled and sustainable independent media and civil society in DRC to have the skills, knowledge and tools they need to reach citizens with accurate and impartial information that promotes inclusion and accountability</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Omprogrammerade medel f&#xF6;r att bek&#xE4;mpa covid-19
Projektet &#xE4;r utformat f&#xF6;r att s&#xE4;kerst&#xE4;lla h&#xE5;llbara politiska reformer samt digitala h&#xE5;llbara oberoende medier och civilsamh&#xE4;lle i DRK. F&#xF6;r att &#xE5;stadkomma detta beh&#xF6;vs tillr&#xE4;cklig kompetens och kunskap samt tillf&#xF6;rlitliga verktyg s&#xE5; att medborgarna erh&#xE5;ller korrekt och opartisk information. Politiska reformer, digitalt aktiverade och h&#xE5;llbara oberoende medier och civilsamh&#xE4;llet i Demokratiska republiken Kongo f&#xF6;r att ha de f&#xE4;rdigheter, kunskap och verktyg som de beh&#xF6;ver f&#xF6;r att n&#xE5; medborgarna med korrekt och opartisk information som fr&#xE4;mjar inkludering och ansvarsutkr&#xE4;vande.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The overall objective of this intervention is&#xA0;to promote a more open and vibrant media sector that contributes to more responsive and transparent institutions in the DRC.
Internews and its local partners will achieve this through the following intermediate results:
1: Legal and regulatory environment for media is strengthened;&#xA0;
2: Targeted media outlets are more independent and professional;
3: Access to high-quality public-interest reporting is increased.</narrative>
  </description>
